author: ekoneil
msg: Complete the move of the system controls from ControlHaus to Apache SVN.

This change includes the Forrest-ized documentation for the controls and the samples for the controls.  None of these samples are wired into the distribution (and likely won't be for 1.0), but the source is now here so that they can be evolved and versioned as part of Beehive.
Thanks to Chad Schoettger for helping get this wired up.
